<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 12 at 7:02AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Slick Roads Possible This Morning...
A convergent boundary has brought some moderate snow and, at
times, some freezing rain this morning creating slicks spots on
roadways. This includes both back roads and main roads.
Be cautious on the roads this morning. Leave extra time to your
destination and include extra space between you and the car in
front of you.</description>
